#. <section class="sutta" id="sn13.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "1. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 9. Pabbatasutta → pabbatūpamasuttaṃ (bj) | pabbatūpama 1 (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn13.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Pabbatasutta"
msgstr "9. A Mountain"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.9:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn13.9:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso himavato pabbatarājassa satta sāsapamattiyo "
"pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhipeyya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a person was to place seven pebbles the size of mustard "
"seeds on the Himalayas, the king of mountains."

msgctxt "sn13.9:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.9:1.4"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yā vā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā "
"upanikkhittā yo vā himavā pabbatarājā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds, or the "
"Himalayas, the king of mountains?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli2.138"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.9:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ yadidaṃ himavā pabbatarājā;"
msgstr "“Sir, the Himalayas, the king of mountains, is certainly more."

msgctxt "sn13.9:2.2"
msgid "appamattikā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā."
msgstr "The seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds are tiny."

msgctxt "sn13.9:2.3"
msgid ""
"Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ "
"upenti himavantaṃ pabbatarājānaṃ upanidhāya satta sāsapamattiyo "
"pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the Himalayas, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a "
"hundred thousandth part.”"

msgctxt "sn13.9:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, for a noble disciple, the suffering that’s over and done "
"with is more …”"

msgctxt "sn13.9:2.5"
msgid "dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.9:2.6"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
